        <li><b>Registration</b>: Accounts are provided via Clerk. Provide accurate information, keep your credentials secure, and you are responsible for activity under your account.</li>
        <li><b>Account actions</b>: We may suspend or terminate accounts for violations, fraud/abuse, or legal/compliance reasons. You may delete your account; see Data and Deletion in our Privacy Policy for effects.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tokens, Pricing, and Payments</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Payments</b>: Purchases and subscriptions are processed by Polar or other payment processors. Taxes may apply. Subscriptions may auto‑renew unless canceled via the customer portal.</li>
        <li><b>Tokens nature</b>: Tokens are virtual credits used in the Services. They have no cash value, are non‑transferable, and are not redeemable for money.</li>
        <li><b>Daily free tokens</b>: We may grant a daily allotment of free tokens (e.g., 10/day). Free tokens <b>do not stack or roll over</b> and may change or be discontinued.</li>
        <li><b>Purchased tokens</b>: Purchased tokens <b>do not expire</b>.</li>
        <li><b>Consumption</b>: Tokens are deducted for generation requests, retries, queued jobs, and may be deducted for partial or failed generations. Costs may vary by model/feature and may change.</li>
        <li><b>Refunds</b>: Monetary refunds are generally <b>not provided</b> once tokens are consumed. We may credit or refund tokens for technical issues (e.g., failed jobs, system errors, extremely degraded quality) including via automatic refunds where implemented.</li>
        <li><b>Adjustments</b>: We may adjust token balances to correct errors or address abuse, fraud, or misuse.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Acceptable Use and Content Policy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Prohibited content and conduct</b>: You may not use the Services to create, upload, or share illegal content; sexual content involving minors; non‑consensual intimate imagery; doxxing; credible threats; incitement; violent extremism; malware; or to infringe IP, trademarks, or rights of publicity/privacy, or to defame.</li>
        <li><b>Safety/accuracy</b>: Outputs may be inaccurate, biased, or unsafe. Do not rely on outputs for medical, legal, or financial decisions. Review before use.</li>
